Package group24.piazzapanic.ui

This package contains code used to draw the UI of the game.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FontHandler
    A convenience class to create fonts that will be used in titles, buttons etc.
    StageAnimation
    Stores an animation, in the form of frames placed around in a texture.
    StageFactory
    Class responsible for creating stages.
    StageManager
    Manages which stage is "active" (ie is displayed and is responding to user input).
    WidgetFactory
    A collection of convenience functions for creating widgets (all static methods).
